summary:
I am a Co-Founder of Crosswise Works, a social enterprise focused on sustainable economic and social development, especially in Africa. We do this by business development of SMEs and the construction of public-private partnerships (PPPs). Our small team is versatile and driven.

Working in a supporting (back-office) role that combines hands-on implementation and content is something that suits me. I have worked on the financial and HRM administration at Crosswise Works since 2017.

I am analytically strong, pragmatic, easy to get along with, and know how to structure things.
